headline.print_headline: Sports Briefing | College Football; North Carolina Knocks Off Pittsburgh

snippet: Marquise Williams threw two long touchdown passes, and visiting North Carolina (7-1, 4-0 Atlantic Coast Conference) beat No. 23 Pittsburgh, 26-19.
abstract: North Carolina defeats Pittsburgh, 26-19, in college football.
